Actor @taapsee, who marks her debut as a producer with her latest OTT film, Blurr, talks about how she reached the decision of backing a dark, edgy thriller like this one and why she has made up her mind to do only lighter projects for some time now. In conversation with HT City Sr Entertainment Editor, @monikarawal99 , the actor admits the dual task of being the lead actor and a producer was sometimes haunting. Taapsee actor also talks about how she doesn't care about satisfying her personal ego and chase secondary things like best actor, highest paid actor or the most variety offering actor.
